  <brief_title>Analysis of the Potentially Parasitocidal Effect of a Long Term Chemotherapy With Benzimidazoles</brief_title>
  <official_title>Analysis of the Potentially Parasitocidal Effect of a Long Term Chemotherapy With Benzimidazoles in Patients With Inoperable Alveolar Echinococcosis Using PET-CT and EmII/3-10 Serology</official_title>
  <sponsors>
